title: #92Noon! Nordo in for PA - Russo/Rock/Leber/Birk
description: --Nordo is in for PA, Michael Russo talks about the Wild's loss of Carson Soucy in the NHL Expansion Draft, Bethel track and field coach Andrew Rock shares his Olympics experience, Ben Leber and Matt Birk make their regular Thursday appearances!
